 S, G\u00f3mez LA, Reyes K, Teresa Leal M |title=A practical demonstration of water disinfection using TiO2 films and sunlight |journal=Water Res. |volume=40 |issue=17 |pages=3274\u201380 |date=October 2006 |pmid=16949121 |doi=10.1016/j.watres.2006.07.006 |url=}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"pmid17998606\">{{cite journal |vauthors=Fisher MB, Keenan CR, Nelson KL, Voelker BM |title=Speeding up solar disinfection (SODIS): effects of hydrogen peroxide, temperature, pH, and copper plus ascorbate on the photoinactivation of E. coli |journal=J Water Health |volume=6 |issue=1 |pages=35\u201351 |date=March 2008 |pmid=17998606 |doi=10.2166/wh.2007.005 |url=}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"pmid18348392\">{{cite journal |author=Mbogo SA |title=A novel technology to improve drinking water quality using natural treatment methods in rural Tanzania |journal=J Environ Health |volume=70 |issue=7 |pages=46\u201350 |date=March 2008 |pmid=18348392 |doi= |url=}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoSB-15\">{{cite journal |vauthors=\u0160\u0107iban M, Kla\u0161nja M, Antov M, \u0160krbi\u0107 B |title= Removal of water turbidity by natural coagulants obtained from chestnut and acorn. |journal= Bioresource Technology |volume= 100 |issue= 24 |pages= 6639\u201343 |year= 2009 |pmid= 19604691 |doi= 10.1016/j.biortech.2009.06.047 }}</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoSB-16\">{{cite journal |last1=Nkurunziza |first1=T |last2=Nduwayezu |first2=JB |last3=Banadda |first3=EN |last4=Nhapi |first4=I |title=The effect of turbidity levels and Moringa oleifera concentration on the effectiveness of coagulation in water treatment. |journal=Water Science and Technology |volume=59 |issue=8 |pages=1551\u20138 |year=2009 |pmid=19403968 |doi=10.2166/wst.2009.155}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoSB-17\">{{cite journal|author1=Byrne JA |author2=Fernandez-Iba\u00f1ez PA |author3=Dunlop PSM |author4=Alrousan DMA |author5=Hamilton JWJ |title=Photocatalytic Enhancement for Solar Disinfection of Water: A Review |journal=International Journal of Photoenergy |year=2011 |do