091419190400.htm ''Clean water at no cost, the SODIS way''], The Hindu, Sep 14, 2006\n* [http://www.physics.org/featuredetail.asp?NewsId=39 A place in the sun] physics.org, October 7, 2009\n* [http://www.wrap.org.uk/downloads/Glass_Wine_bottles_and_UV_light.c70cc017.5719.pdf Glass Bottles and UV Light] ([[PDF]]) provides data on how much UV light is filtered by various types of glass bottles, August 2008\n\n[[Category:Appropriate technology]]\n[[Category:Survival skills]]\n[[Category:Water treatment]]\n[[Category:Water supply]]\n[[Category:Repurposing]]\n", "name_user": "Iridescent", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eApplications:Cleanup andtypo fixing,typo(s) fixed: \u2019s \u2192 's", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Solar_water_disinfection"}
